title: When the Impostor clutch fails... - Among Us #Shorts
author: Kromus
description:
-When your Imposter teammate gets voted out early in the round and you go to do your best to try and win.... it doesn't work most of the time jus like this one lol. Regardless we had fun like we always do in game. As always I hope you enjoy the video!!!
- If you like what you see, think about maybe subscribing to the channel for more funny game content!!!
